## Memory Tool

### Basic Usage

\`\`\`typescript
const response = await client.messages.create({
  model: "{{OPUS_ID}}",
  max_tokens: 2048,
  messages: [
    {
      role: "user",
      content: "Remember that my preferred language is TypeScript.",
