<!--
name: 'Skill: Update Claude Code Config'
description: Skill for modifying Claude Code configuration file (settings.json).
ccVersion: 2.1.9
variables:
  - SETTINGS_FILE_LOCATION_PROMPT
  - HOOKS_CONFIGURATION_PROMPT
